no matter what the consequences are in my ventures
I shall be strong and i will say this boldly
forever into the minds of those i love and loathe...
you will know of my pain and my problems
my angst is forever held true
not to be taken lightly anymore
no more shall jessi be trodden on
taken advantage of
pushed around
or yelled at by bitches who have no authority
not to be told what to do by those who do not matter in my life

those who have pained me in some way
attacking them in their sleep
when i die i will be free of them all.....

that is my life story written out it is the new prophecy of my path.... join me and be nice or die on the outskirts of mere reality

Passing by the shattered glass
Of what her life used to be
She saw so much change
Her attitude changed from that of a depressed child
To one of a person who has no fears or anger
She hadn't noticed the one thing that stood in her way
They were against them every day
So she stood up tall and swept the glass away
And yelled so loud that everyone could hear
She yelled You cant keep me down anymore, 
Im coming out a new person
And with that she began to see her life more clearly
That she didnt suck, her mental breakdowns didnt help her any
And that she could love herself without anger or fear

Pray for the one who has been hurt
Pray for them as if they will never live again
Even if it only lasts but a day pray for them
You could be the one thing saving them from eternal damnation
You could rescue them from something horrible
But then again who really takes their own time to do good for others?
I know of nobody who does that
Not one single person who really truly wants to help others
Actually only one person
They are good inside and out.
Be like them and help others
Listen you crazies for this could be your one chance to help someone else!

Perfect

People only care about how you look
If you aren't perfect you arent their friend
Menacing Mistress perfection is
Its all about how you act and how you look
If you arent a size zero you are nothing
If you arent popular people want you murdered
If you are a little different people hate you
Why can't people accept everyone for who they are
If you don't love people for who they are you suck
If you are skinny and say you are fat
YOU NEED HELP

GET MORE HELP
Don't try to be perfect... 
Only barbie is and shes fake
Grade A bullshit
What every person wants to be is skinny....
Load of shit in my opinion
Dont try to be something you cant be, just be yourself
People love originality....
Well they used to at least

...sleep...

sleep engulf me
take me away to a land of pretend
you enlighten my heart
make me feel confident
make me feel safe
you help me through my tough times
and ease me through my great moments
you are my savior
the one that is my one and only
nothing makes me happier 
only to fall into internal darkness

this is inspired by A.D.D from System of a Down



Go away
Let me be
I do not wish to see you here anymore
You are the reason for my problems
I hate you
I fear for you
I cry over you
I fall over dying in your arms
This is my undoing
Your cause and effect on me has led to deadly consequences
I won't let you topple my happiness
My happiness means to little to you
Yet your happiness means the world to me
I'd be willing to give up everything
Just so you won't ever be sad
So you won't ever feel pain 
So you won't ever cry
Yet you don't give a shit about what I feel.
When will you learn?
When will you care?
When will you love me for me?
When will you see the destructive person you've become to me?

wow i wrote that whole thing in 5-10 minutes... i could get another out... i love that poem!



Another one, no name


You looked right through me
As if I was air
You messed with my emotions
You act so horrible to me
Yet I still love you no matter what you do to me
Maybe I am naive, or stupid but that can't change my emotions
You are always around yet you arent really there for me
You walk right by me without a second glance
I wave to get your attention
Yet you don't notice
I scream your name yet you still don't hear me
When will you learn I will always be trying to grab your attention?
I'll be there for you through thick and thin.
Sadness and sorrow.
Love and Hate.
You never knew this but you are my shining light, 
My light at the end of the tunnel,
My shining light to guide me through everything,
When my world is falling I turn to you for guidance
For support and help yet you do not care
How would it feel for me to not care for you?
I bet you wouldnt even notice anything.
I'll continue on as if you are all that matters to me!

Those who look deep in my eyes see hurt
They see the rejction from past and present loved ones
They show little to no compassion for the hurt one
She cries when nobody watches
Screams when shes alone
Wanting, Praying, Hoping to be noticed and loved for herself
Always helping others before her own self
Forgetting her own needs
Wanting others to succeed more
Hoping for recognition.... it never comes 
Yet she waits, ever hopeful someone will hear her plea
One day she will die from loving others yet not being loved enough 
Nobody will miss her she will rot underground
unhappy, unloved, and truly betrayed.
